168  initial_alignment.getAlignedCloud(scan_cloud_aligned);
169 
170  if (!Utils::isValidCloud(scan_cloud_aligned)) return 0;

173  GICPAlignment gicp_alignment(cad_cloud_filtered, scan_cloud_aligned);

249  }
250 
251  if (publish_fods)

259  }

269  ros::spinOnce();
